TRAVELER'S PROPERTY CASUALTY COMPANY OF AMERICA
v.
ACTAVIS S245867 Supreme Court of California. SEPTEMBER 26, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 4/3. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for Liberty Surplus Insurance Corp. v. Ledesma and Meyer Construction Co. (2018) 5 Cal.5th 216, 233 Cal.Rptr.3d 487, 418 P.3d 400, is dismissed. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).) Corrigan, J., was recused and did not participate.
